:: 0) Normalize Windows CRLF to LF (kills hidden \r)
"\r\n"->"\n"

:: 1) Convert non-breaking spaces to normal spaces (VERY common in web/ChatGPT copies)
"\u00A0"gu->" "

:: 2) Remove trailing spaces (prevents “blank” lines that aren’t blank)
"(?m)[ \t]+$"->"TRIM"x

:: 3) Delete whitespace-only lines (lines that look blank but contain spaces)
"(?m)^[ \t]+$"->"EMPTY"x

:: 4) Convert bullet symbol • into real Markdown list bullets, preserving indentation
"(?m)^([ \t]*)•[ \t]+"gmu->"$1- "

:: 5) Remove blank lines *between* list items (makes lists compact/nice)
"(?m)^([ \t]*- .+)\n\n(?=[ \t]*- )"gmu->"$1\n"

:: 6) Finally, collapse any remaining 2+ blank lines to a single blank line
"\n{3,}"->"\n\n"
